Template Builder zoomed canvas toolbar width fix:
- Time: 2026-05-11 KST.
- Root cause:
  - At high preview zoom, the canvas component grid item kept its default `min-width:auto`, so the large `.phone-canvas` min-content width expanded the stage column.
  - Because `.stage-toolbar` is in the same stage column, it visually grew with the zoomed canvas.
- Decision:
  - Keep the toolbar in the fixed stage column.
  - Let only the canvas component host handle overflow/scroll by setting the workspace stage/canvas grid items to `min-width:0` and the canvas host to `overflow:auto`.
- Changed files:
  - `clipper_angular/src/features/template-builder/components/template-builder-workspace.component.scss`
  - `clipper_angular/src/features/template-builder/components/template-builder-canvas.component.scss`
